/*
 * MOT SpotWelder with Arduino Nano and SSR
 * 
 * impulse Values 1-20x
 * preweld Time Values 0-300 ms
 * pause Time Values 0-500 ms
 * weld Time Values 0-1000 ms
 * pause befor new 0-150 ms
 * 
 * // if weld Time = 0 => Manualweld //just now without funktion
 * 
 * Displayed value/10ms only
 * 
 * Simple Click -> Settings
 * Double Click -> Load from EEprom
 * Triple Click -> Save to EEprom
 * ----
 * in Settings: 
 *      1 Click: Esc, continue without new settings
 *      2 Click: Enter, store the setting
 *      3 Click: Nope
 * Cheat: from Settings/Weldtime  with Longclick step into SecretMenu
 * 
 * in SecretMenu
 *  can be set 50/60Hz basis (name Hz)
 *  SinusMax delay for ZeroCross ± 1/(4*Hz) setting (ca. ±5000µsec)
 *  
 * ----
 * 
